pi-doctor explain throttling
Firmware and thermal analysis
  CPU temperature: unavailable

Assessment
  `vcgencmd` is missing, so firmware throttle telemetry could not be read.
  Why this matters: under-voltage and firmware throttling history live in Raspberry Pi firmware telemetry.
  What to run next: install Raspberry Pi firmware utilities or run this on Raspberry Pi OS, then retry.
